CommBuf * Hypertable::RangeServerProtocol::create_request_update ( const TableIdentifier &  table,
uint32_t  count,
StaticBuffer &  buffer,
uint32_t  flags 
) [static]

Creates an "update" request message.

The data argument holds a sequence of key/value pairs. Each key/value pair is encoded as two variable lenght ByteStringrecords back-to-back. This method transfers ownership of the data buffer to the CommBuf that gets returned.
